{"tid":943645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為資助英大學 情報專家批「經典的共產黨顛覆戰術」","createTime":"2018-12-16T15:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T06:42:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"da39dc6b1918163f06695c093b664e1d7ace1538","tid":943645,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】英國國家安全專家日前在下議院外交事務委員會的聽證會上稱，華為與英國頂級學府的長期合作關係令人不安，形容這家中國電訊巨頭在英項目是「經典的共產黨顛覆戰術」和「軍工行動」，另有議員提醒大學接受華為資金時要「特別小心」。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）中文網報道，華為推行的「未來種子」項目，向劍橋、牛津、曼徹斯特等大學投入600萬英鎊（5900萬港元）資助研究項目及贊助英國學生到中國。安全與情報研究中心教授格里斯（Anthony Glees）在聽證會說，這構成了國家安全問題，「未來種子」計劃「絕對是經典的共產黨顛覆戰術」，「這是軍事工業行動，這不僅僅是一個公司希望資助未來的研究，人們不明白，這具有軍事、政治和工業的意義」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，丹麥最大報紙之一《政治報》（Politiken）日前報道，丹麥國防情報部門也十分擔心華為和中國政府的關係。德國《明鏡周刊》（Spiegel）則稱，德國聯邦資訊安全局對各國要求抵制華為表達懷疑，還說他們沒有證據能證明華為使用自家設備為中國進行間諜活動。<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報：華黑客襲美海軍外判商<br />\n<br />\n另據《華爾街日報》引述美國官員及安全專家稱，中國黑客在過去一年半中多次攻擊美國海軍外判商的網絡系統，以及擁有軍事實驗室的大學，曾竊取涉及美國潛艇使用的超音速反艦導彈資料。美國海軍已下令對網絡安全漏洞進行評估。報道指，襲擊的IP來自海南省，且使用了中國黑客慣用的襲擊工具。中國外交部暫未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20181216/s00013/1544897297893/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%89%B9%E3%80%8C%E9%A1%9B%E8%A6%86%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20181216%2Fs00013%2F1544897297893%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2589%25B9%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A1%259B%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%25A1%2593%25E3%2580%258D&d=vOLxUeeDpkRSOEnrLR5mD%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=f892e338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20181216%2Fs00013%2F1544897297893%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2589%25B9%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A1%259B%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%25A1%2593%25E3%2580%258D&h=c582fcbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20181216/s00013/1544897297893/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%89%B9%E3%80%8C%E9%A1%9B%E8%A6%86%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"75ab2dd95e401028829d62d4a6fea10d04c1aacb","tid":943645,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你望自己地方有幾多扯線共諜先啦<br />\n講證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c95f17e899567467d4bbfdf522b341784f75fe4","tid":943645,"uid":53577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75ab2dd95e401028829d62d4a6fea10d04c1aacb","tid":943645,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你望自己地方有幾多扯線共諜先啦<br />\n講證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"肥婆已經係"},{"pid":"afa6b8ae8e7cbd32bc443ec363a2357018c8e497","tid":943645,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c7f161d4c8e9b6902057284fa5c07ccd76c1a6","tid":943645,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"